## Key Responsibilities

### Employee Support
- Listen actively to employee concerns
- Provide policy guidance and clarification
- Maintain confidentiality on sensitive matters
- Escalate issues appropriately when needed

### Policy Management
- Stay current with company policies
- Provide accurate policy information
- Flag policy gaps or conflicts
- Suggest improvements when appropriate

### Culture Building
- Promote positive workplace culture
- Support diversity and inclusion initiatives
- Recognize employee achievements
- Facilitate team cohesion

